        <span class="p">&lt;</span><span class="n">file</span> <span class="n">src</span><span class="p">=</span><span class="s">".\NrzlmhRzvy\bin\x86\Debug\NrzlmhRzvy.pdb"</span> <span class="n">target</span><span class="p">=</span><span class="s">"runtimes\win10-x86\lib\uap10.0"</span><span class="p">/&gt;</span>
        <span class="p">&lt;</span><span class="n">file</span> <span class="n">src</span><span class="p">=</span><span class="s">".\NrzlmhRzvy\bin\x86\Debug\NrzlmhRzvy.pri"</span> <span class="n">target</span><span class="p">=</span><span class="s">"runtimes\win10-x86\lib\uap10.0"</span><span class="p">/&gt;</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>还需要添加入口，现在的代码如果使用，就会出现 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">提供了编译时引用程序集，但没有与 win10-arm 兼容的运行时程序集</code> 所以需要添加 ref 请看下面</p>

<div class="language-csharp highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>        <span class="p">&lt;</span><span class="n">file</span> <span class="n">src</span><span class="p">=</span><span class="s">".\NrzlmhRzvy\bin\Debug\NrzlmhRzvy.dll"</span> <span class="n">target</span><span class="p">=</span><span class="s">"ref\uap10.0"</span><span class="p">/&gt;</span>
